Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:17.97,Staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs32}字幕製作：澄空學園 × 華盟字幕社
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.65,0:03:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.65,0:03:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們真的要過上沒有後輩的高中生活了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.64,0:03:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.25,0:03:29.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是覺得那樣也挺好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.27,0:03:31.24,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,900)\pos(271,601)} #8     「想做的事是」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.34,0:03:32.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之在校園觀摩上開演唱會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.42,0:03:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能通過這樣來增加新生數量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.19,0:03:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這之後學生會採取獨立行動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.85,0:03:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想方設法阻止廢校
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.47,0:03:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.39,0:03:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.63,0:03:48.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼要說的說出來比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.62,0:03:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.81,0:03:54.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  這次協商討論的是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.85,0:03:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎樣做才能增加新生的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.48,0:03:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.18,0:04:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話就多介紹點有意思的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.48,0:04:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然學校歷史和師資力量也很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.82,0:04:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我覺得以往的學生會有點太死板了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.24,0:04:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如說這裡的校服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.12,0:04:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不少人都說很好看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.63,0:04:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個不錯  來把這種優點展現出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.52,0:04:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學園偶像很受歡迎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.79,0:04:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯哦  我們學校也有  是繆斯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.15,0:04:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託她們開一場演唱會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.82,0:04:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.90,0:04:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.77,0:04:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.49,0:04:35.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.60,0:04:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  意外地很受外校學生歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.26,0:04:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個稍微有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.11,0:04:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學生會長？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.31,0:04:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.50,0:04:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是學園偶像的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.60,0:05:00.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.33,0:05:03.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好  接下來有校園觀摩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.54,0:05:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以的話希望你們來開場演唱會…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.52,0:05:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.32,0:05:08.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還什麼都沒有決定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.70,0:05:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.90,0:05:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2 3 4 5 6 7 8
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.02,0:05:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.12,0:05:21.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  大家都很完美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.49,0:05:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  這下能趕得上校園觀摩了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.70,0:05:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是真的能開演唱會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.12,0:05:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被學生會長阻止的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.21,0:05:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那點沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.74,0:05:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定會有介紹社團的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.85,0:05:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那時候唱歌的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.75,0:05:37.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.78,0:05:40.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,節奏還沒對上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.58,0:05:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海未
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.39,0:05:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了  再練習一次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.08,0:05:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2 3 4 5 6 7 8
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.28,0:05:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.84,0:05:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.82,0:05:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們終於追上仁子的等級了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.04,0:05:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.33,0:06:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒辦法比現在更好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.52,0:06:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.47,0:06:06.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就現在這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.48,0:06:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底對什麼不滿意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.35,0:06:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說清楚點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.05,0:06:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法讓人感動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.65,0:06:15.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果就憑現在這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.97,0:06:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海未…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.23,0:06:21.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向學生會長？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.82,0:06:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  海未說要去學舞蹈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.31,0:06:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  看了她的芭蕾後我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.44,0:06:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的舞蹈還遠遠不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.33,0:06:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說有事  就這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.66,0:06:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是學生會長對我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.07,0:06:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭吧  絕對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.10,0:06:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在嫉妒吧  嫉妒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.36,0:06:43.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前也覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.43,0:06:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.20,0:06:46.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能理解一個那麼擅長跳舞的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.68,0:06:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了我們的表演後說我們是外行的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.69,0:06:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.04,0:06:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我反對  說不定會被她毀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.76,0:07:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  高三生有我仁子一個就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.53,0:07:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學生會長  有點可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.32,0:07:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡有趣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.04,0:07:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.78,0:07:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒覺得不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.78,0:07:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.20,0:07:16.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為  身邊有個舞蹈很好的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.98,0:07:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們想要跳得更好的話就得去請教她沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.44,0:07:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話是這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.57,0:07:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的話  我贊成
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.58,0:07:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穗乃果
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.77,0:07:26.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試著拜託一下她啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.52,0:07:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.68,0:07:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.99,0:07:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有點想看繪里學姐的舞蹈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.16,0:07:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.63,0:07:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那明天去問她一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.22,0:07:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會變成什麼樣我可不管
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.41,0:07:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣  歷史悠久的音木坂學院
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.99,0:07:52.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直促進著本地的發展
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.34,0:07:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有  當時的學院還被稱為音樂學院
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.94,0:08:01.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學院內有很多以藝術家為目標的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.23,0:08:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有著創造性十足的氛圍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.93,0:08:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這所音木坂學院裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.94,0:08:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,體重增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.77,0:08:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.91,0:08:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  很無聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.29,0:08:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.66,0:08:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後半段非常吸引我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.99,0:08:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會在校園觀摩那天前修正的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.71,0:08:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別客氣  隨便說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.82,0:08:28.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得沒意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.20,0:08:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.12,0:08:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼姐姐要說這些話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.19,0:08:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我不想廢校
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.65,0:08:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不希望音木坂消失
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.43,0:08:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.51,0:08:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是姐姐想做的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.86,0:08:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會討厭的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.23,0:08:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的學校要是被廢校的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.37,0:08:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話是這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.13,0:08:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你為了阻止廢校過分勉強自己了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.28,0:09:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.93,0:09:01.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勉強自己…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.35,0:09:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繪里真固執
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.26,0:09:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想讓學校延續下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.79,0:09:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.55,0:09:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我教你們舞蹈？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.25,0:09:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  能教我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.38,0:09:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們想跳得更好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.38,0:09:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不想被你說得那麼差勁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.51,0:09:34.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.51,0:09:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.75,0:09:38.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不能贊同你們的活動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.56,0:09:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不可否認你們很受歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.39,0:09:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.67,0:09:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然要做就要請你們努力達到我的標準
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.23,0:09:49.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.37,0:09:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.60,0:09:54.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.33,0:09:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有不祥的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.64,0:10:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星辰開始移動了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.24,0:10:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LOVELIVE!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.89,0:10:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絢瀨同學  很遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.61,0:10:33.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又失敗了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.16,0:10:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.67,0:10:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.47,0:10:40.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用在意這種選拔會的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.75,0:10:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小凜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.49,0:10:50.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.36,0:10:51.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.82,0:10:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真虧你們能走到今天這一步
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.79,0:10:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.84,0:10:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天還好好的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.42,0:10:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們因為基礎沒有打好所以才會洋相百出的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.97,0:11:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把腿打開
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.00,0:11:02.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.51,0:11:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛喵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.92,0:11:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣  保持腿部張開的姿勢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.09,0:11:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少要讓腹部碰到地板才行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.19,0:11:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提高柔軟性關係到一切
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.93,0:11:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先要讓你們全員能做到這點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.31,0:11:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去的話正式演出會很懸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.62,0:11:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不祥的預感  命中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.57,0:11:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.23,0:11:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是佩服的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.23,0:11:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都能做到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.53,0:11:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想靠舞蹈把人迷住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.77,0:11:35.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做到這種事也是理所應當
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.24,0:11:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有10分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.53,0:11:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.91,0:11:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肌肉訓練重新再練一次比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.14,0:11:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後再來一組
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.79,0:11:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花陽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.28,0:11:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花陽  你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.36,0:11:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.05,0:12:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了  今天就到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.81,0:12:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.17,0:12:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也不用那樣說話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.96,0:12:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是進行了冷靜的判斷而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.56,0:12:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們多少也應該知道自己的實力了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.84,0:12:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的校園觀摩關係到學校的存亡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你們做不到就早說吧  別浪費時間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.61,0:12:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.62,0:12:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.71,0:12:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天也請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.83,0:12:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.70,0:12:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞里沙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.76,0:12:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.10,0:12:47.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借我聽聽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.84,0:12:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢  看著繆斯的演唱會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.01,0:12:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心裡就會感受到一陣暖意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.65,0:13:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼拼命努力  又非常享受的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.33,0:13:04.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.21,0:13:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然比起姐姐是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.11,0:13:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我非常受到她們的鼓舞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.32,0:13:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.58,0:13:21.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.38,0:13:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.76,0:13:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.09,0:13:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在偷看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.88,0:13:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.63,0:13:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.82,0:13:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.76,0:13:42.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先做柔軟體操是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.52,0:13:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不累嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.56,0:13:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天做了那樣的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.19,0:13:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天又要做同樣的事情了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.70,0:13:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且根本就不知道能不能做好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.82,0:13:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們想去做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.91,0:13:58.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然練習的確很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.69,0:14:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全身酸疼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.34,0:14:03.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是想要阻止廢校的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.70,0:14:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是不會輸給學生會長的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.91,0:14:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  今天也請多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.01,0:14:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學生會長！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.39,0:14:27.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是姐姐想做的事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.61,0:14:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們想去做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.08,0:14:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢  看著繆斯的演唱會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.97,0:14:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心裡就會感受到一陣暖意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.44,0:14:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼拼命努力  又非常享受的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.60,0:14:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.41,0:14:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.73,0:14:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了繪里的朋友  又在學生會工作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.25,0:14:47.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在想一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.93,0:14:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繪里真正想做的事情究竟是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.33,0:14:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為一直在一起  我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.00,0:14:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繪里總是為了別人在努力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.41,0:15:02.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以看起來好像一直在忍耐著什麼似的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.62,0:15:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒有考慮自己的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.78,0:15:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要讓學校保留下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.88,0:15:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是因為學生會長的義務感吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.17,0:15:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以理事長才沒有贊成你的行動不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.70,0:15:20.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繪里的  繪里真正想做的事情是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.43,0:15:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  再來一次
